description: Deletes the key value pair specified by the key.

parameters.name: KvsARN
parameters.description: The Amazon Resource Name (ARN) of the Key Value Store.

parameters.name: IfMatch
parameters.description: The current version (ETag) of the Key Value Store that you are deleting keys from, which you can get using DescribeKeyValueStore.

nested_items.name: ItemCount
nested_items.description: Number of key value pairs in the Key Value Store after the successful delete.

nested_items.name: TotalSizeInBytes
nested_items.description: Total size of the Key Value Store after the successful delete, in bytes.

nested_items.name: ETag
nested_items.description: The current version identifier of the Key Value Store after the successful delete.
